Author information:
(1)Irish Melanoma Group, Colman K. Byrnes Research Centre, Beaumont Hospital, 
Dublin, Ireland.

Both coumarin (1,2-benzopyrone) and warfarin (4-hydroxycoumarin) have been shown 
to prevent the recurrence of malignant melanoma. Their action is 
macrophage-dependent and the dosage is critical. In 1984 a multicentre, 
